Common.Strapline.Common.Text: A-GRADE OFFICE ASSET WITH STRONG OCCUPANCY

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
61 Park Road is a two level commercial office building with basement parking, situated directly opposite the popular and trendy cafe precinct of Milton.

This Level 1 tenancy is currently undergoing a full refurbishment allowing a prospective tenants to design and create their own fit out for the long term in a secure and reputable position.

Multiple public transport options are within easy reach and the Brisbane CBD is just a short drive away. The tenancy has an allocation of 10 car bays at prevailing market rates.

Distinguish your business on one of Brisbane's most famous Streets and you won't look back.
